tree-into-ssa.c (rewrite_update_stmt): Do not dump extra newlines.

2011-12-21  Martin Jambor  <mjambor@suse.cz>

	* tree-into-ssa.c (rewrite_update_stmt): Do not dump extra newlines.
	(rewrite_update_enter_block): Likewise.
